      "$id": "0ce3b4ed-8457-512e-8426-4243622339cf",
      "code": "self.self = /* ? */;\nif ((parent && SSF2API.isReady()) || self.self) {\n\tSSF2API.playSound(\"jiggs_crouch\");\n}\nreturn;",
