      "$id": "c7483a5b-de10-5e54-86e6-e9863e1c3474",
      "code": "self.controlCheckCount = 0;\nself.self = /* ? */;\nif (SSF2API.isReady() && self.self) {\n}\nif (/* ? */) {\n\tself.dir = self.self.isFacingRight();\n\tself.ground = self.self.isOnGround();\n}\nreturn;",
